# ─── Internal seeding / e2e tooling (not public project code) ───
# DEPLOY NOTE: mainnet_seed.py + feedback.py are required by the agent at RUNTIME (demo rotation →
# ERC-8004 giveFeedback / 8004scan). `railway up` respects THIS file (not .railwayignore), so it
# excludes them from the image and the demo rotation ImportErrors on boot. To deploy: temporarily
# comment out the mainnet_seed.py + feedback.py lines below, run `railway up`, then restore. See
# agent/DEPLOY.md. Keep them out of the public GitHub repo — do NOT `git add` them.
agent/scripts/mainnet_seed.py
agent/scripts/submit_feedback.py
agent/scripts/mainnet_e2e.py
agent/src/feedback.py
config/e2e_run.mainnet.json

